A cyberpunk cityscape at night with towering holographic billboards displaying streams of glowing data - IP addresses, browser icons, and operating system symbols cascading like digital rain. In the foreground, a lone figure walks down a neon-lit alley, their silhouette reflected in rain-soaked pavement, completely unaware that massive floating digital eyes hover above the buildings, scanning and tracking movement. The atmosphere is moody with deep purples, electric blues, and hot pink neon reflections, conveying surveillance and digital exposure in an urban jungle of glass and chrome.
